{"tid":1255803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"６２６　設定目標：數十萬參與集會","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:13:30.000Z","uid":268656,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9484201ba6a0b7060e10999886670a471c20e743","tid":1255803,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">首先要向所有前線義士，<br />\n包括曾經係６１２食過彈中過槍＋包圍立法會＋警總＋政府建築物既朋友，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>致崇高敬意</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">反送中運動發展到今日，<br />\n４大早有共識既訴求，而且係太古烈士既遺願：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回惡法</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追究濫權警察暴行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">釋放學生傷者</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撤回定性暴動</span><br />\n到現在，我地依然奮戰到底，因為一樣都未爭取到。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為何要數十萬人參加集會？</strong></span><br />\n無可否認，＂數量＂係我方其中一個最大既武器，<br />\n我地要將分散左既群眾，當中包括極大數量既淺黃淺藍，<br />\n用一種比較溫和既集會形式，係Ｇ２０開幕之前，重新凝聚民意，<br />\n而民意可以直接有效地傳送到世界各地民主國家，包括開會地方日本，<br />\n結合本地文宣組與國外傳媒多方面施壓，保持對我方有利既聲量。<br />\n<br />\n根據過往晚間集會（非遊行）經驗，參加人數約略過十萬，<br />\n六位數字（十進制）依然係一個有影響力既數字。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如何達到？我地要突破同溫層</span></strong><br />\n<strong>１.認真，連登有冇可能組織到街站團</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1254865/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1254865/page/1</a><br />\n[由連登核心推出社區] 落地落區谷集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1255491/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1255491/page/1</a><br />\n突破同溫層，重建淺黃淺藍對爭取４大目標既信心，<br />\n抗衡建制親中抹黑打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 加入文宣，主動提出建議，或者推POST／分享至各大社交平台</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/search?q=%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3&amp;type=desc_create_time\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/search?q=%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3&amp;type=desc_create_time</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/c9ovFM4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9ovFM4.png&h=0dc8ff53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. ６２６出黎！叫埋朋友同學親人！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>６２６之後？</strong></span><br />\n老老實實，再等到６２８（星期五）先做野，隔左咁多日意民肯定會再減退，<br />\n６２６既成果會成為之後行動既新基礎，<br />\n明白６２７同６２８既安排會讓各位感到攰，<br />\n大家頂住！<br />\n<br />\n如果有整體行動上既建議，請大家多多發表，力求完美。</div>"},{"pid":"590d00786ca0a02c74388abae3213ed88dc1deef","tid":1255803,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fc241cdb0ca60ad022486a3d5580e5a0def7f73","tid":1255803,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a3408a7b70c9f0eb37e38b1fe6c39c405ca3d9c","tid":1255803,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}